---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/site/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/site/Footer.astro";
import CTABanner from "../components/blocks/CTABanner.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About ViFi | AI Phone Assistant for Small Business"
  description="ViFi answers your business calls and sends you a recap of every conversation. Here's the thinking behind the product."
>
  <div class="flex min-h-screen flex-col">
    <Header />
    <main class="flex-1">
      <section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
          <h1
            class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6"
          >
            About <span
              class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-transparent"
              >ViFi</span
            >
          </h1>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
            <p>
              Small business owners miss calls every day. They're with a
              customer, on a job site, or driving between appointments. The
              phone rings, nobody answers, and the caller moves on.
            </p>

            <p>
              We built ViFi because answering the call is only half the
              problem. The other half is knowing what happened on the call
              before you follow up.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-text pt-4">
              What ViFi does
            </h2>

            <p>
              ViFi answers your business calls with a professional voice,
              talks with the caller, and then sends you a complete recap:
              a short summary, the full transcript, and a recording. When
              you call back, you already know what was said and what needs
              to happen next.
            </p>

            <p>
              No guessing, no "sorry, remind me what you called about."
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-text pt-4">
              Who it's for
            </h2>

            <p>
              ViFi is built for businesses where the phone drives revenue:
              contractors, medical practices, law firms, real estate agents,
              and anyone who can't afford to miss a call or return one
              unprepared.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-text pt-4">
              How we think about it
            </h2>

            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>
                <strong class="text-text">The callback matters most.</strong> We
                built ViFi around what happens after the conversation, not during it.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong class="text-text">Professional voice, not a phone tree.</strong> Callers
                talk to an AI that sounds like your front desk, not a robot.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong class="text-text">Two-minute setup.</strong> Forward your
                calls and you're live. No hardware, no IT.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-text pt-4">
              Get in touch
            </h2>

            <p>
              ViFi is in early access. If you'd like to try it or learn more,
              reach out at
              <a
                href="mailto:hello@vifi.us"
                class="text-primary hover:text-secondary transition-colors"
                >hello@vifi.us</a
              >.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <CTABanner
        heading="Ready to stop missing calls?"
        description="Try ViFi free for 7 days. See what a proper call recap looks like."
      />
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </div>

  <div class="pointer-events-none fixed inset-0 -z-10" aria-hidden="true">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 20% 10%, rgba(108,99,255,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%), radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 80%, rgba(0,212,170,0.10) 0%, transparent 60%);"
    >
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
